============
INSTRUCTIONS
============


USING THIS THEME ON BLOGGER
------------------------------------------------------------

1. Download the theme and extract the zip file to some location

2. Log in to your Blogger dashboard and go to Layout > Edit HTML

3. Ensure you back up your old theme in case you decide to use it again. To do this, click on the "Download Full Template" link and save the file to your hard drive.

4. Under "Backup/Restore Template", click the "Browse" button.

5. Browse to the location of your theme and click OK.

6. Click the "Upload" button.

7. The HTML of your new theme will now appear in the box below. You can preview your theme or simply save to start using it!

8. Enjoy!